## Safety Measures

### Non-Negotiables
1. **Full backup BEFORE any processing**
2. **NO automatic deletion** - All removals go to staging first
3. **Integrity checks** on every file before processing
4. **Original files preserved** until conversion verified
5. **Audit log** of all actions taken

### Verification Checkpoints
- [ ] Backup verified (file count + size match)
- [ ] All files pass integrity check
- [ ] Inventory complete and reviewed
- [ ] Sample conversions verified manually
- [ ] Duplicate report reviewed
- [ ] User approves cleanup decisions
- [ ] Staging folder reviewed before deletion
- [ ] Final file count reconciliation

