## Handling Handwritten Content

Since Notability files are primarily handwritten:

**Option A: Extract Only (Recommended for now)**
- Pull out embedded PDFs and images
- Create Markdown stubs linking to assets
- Handwriting preserved as images/PDFs

**Option B: OCR Conversion (Future)**
- Use OCR to convert handwriting to text
- Requires: Tesseract or cloud OCR service
- Quality depends on handwriting legibility
- Can be done later on extracted images

**Recommendation:** Start with Option A. You'll have all your content in portable formats. OCR can be applied later to specific important notes.

